uk.ac.ebi.pride.utilities.data.controller.impl.Transformer

Class MzTabTransformer

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.ebi.pride.utilities.data.controller.impl.Transformer.MzTabTransformer

  • public class MzTabTransformer
extends Object
    MzTab Transformer to ms-data-core-api Objects. We are only converting proteins and psm without the peptide information in the first release. In the near future we will also convert peptide information.
    Author:
    Yasset Perez-Riverol, Rui Wang
